510
00:25:28,562 --> 00:25:29,843
So, to close this up.

511
00:25:31,495 --> 00:25:34,317
The system that we created in our method served our purposes

512
00:25:34,377 --> 00:25:34,798
quite well.

513
00:25:35,318 --> 00:25:38,801
A team that never created a quest-based game before managed

514
00:25:38,821 --> 00:25:42,604
to create almost 150 quests of various complexity.

